### Login

This endpoint allows users to log in and obtain an access token.

#### Request Body

- This request requires a form-data body type.


#### Response

- **Status:** 200

- **Content-Type:** application/json

- { "data": { "id": "", "name": "", "email": "", "account_type": "", "admin_group_id": null, "created_at": "", "updated_at": "" }, "access_token": "", "token_type": "", "expires_in": 0}


#### Example Response

``` json
{
  "data": {
    "id": "",
    "name": "",
    "email": "",
    "account_type": "",
    "admin_group_id": null,
    "created_at": "",
    "updated_at": ""
  },
  "access_token": "",
  "token_type": "",
  "expires_in": 0
}

 ```

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": { "type": "string" },
        "name": { "type": "string" },
        "email": { "type": "string" },
        "account_type": { "type": "string" },
        "admin_group_id": { "type": ["string", "null"] },
        "created_at": { "type": "string" },
        "updated_at": { "type": "string" }
      }
    },
    "access_token": { "type": "string" },
    "token_type": { "type": "string" },
    "expires_in": { "type": "integer" }
  }
}

 ```

### Create User Profile

This endpoint allows the user to create a new user profile.

#### Request Body

- Form-Data

    - No parameters


#### Response

The response is a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": {"type": "string"},
        "name": {"type": "string"},
        "email": {"type": "string"},
        "account_type": {"type": "string"},
        "admin_group_id": {"type": ["string", "null"]},
        "created_at": {"type": "string"},
        "updated_at": {"type": "string"}
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

### Register User

Creates a new user account.

#### Request Body

- Type: JSON

    - name (string): The name of the user.

    - email (string): The email of the user.

    - password (string): The password for the user account.

    - password_confirmation (string): The confirmation of the password.


#### Response

- Content-Type: application/json

- Status: 201

- { "data": { "id": "", "name": "", "email": "", "account_type": "", "admin_group_id": null, "created_at": "", "updated_at": "" }, "access_token": "", "token_type": "", "expires_in": 0}


#### Response JSON Schema

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": {"type": "string"},
        "name": {"type": "string"},
        "email": {"type": "string"},
        "account_type": {"type": "string"},
        "admin_group_id": {"type": ["null", "string"]},
        "created_at": {"type": "string"},
        "updated_at": {"type": "string"}
      }
    },
    "access_token": {"type": "string"},
    "token_type": {"type": "string"},
    "expires_in": {"type": "number"}
  }
}

 ```
